statements: SELECT * FROM ai_impact_analysis;
SELECT id, decision_name FROM ai_impact_analysis;
SELECT societal_group FROM ai_impact_analysis WHERE id = 1;
SELECT impact_description FROM ai_impact_analysis ORDER BY decision_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM ai_impact_analysis WHERE societal_group = 'community';
SELECT impact_description, decision_name, societal_group FROM ai_impact_analysis WHERE societal_group = 'Government'
SELECT * FROM ai_impact_analysis ORDER BY decision_name DESC
SELECT id, impact_description FROM ai_impact_analysis WHERE id < 100 OR impact_description LIKE '%positive%'
SELECT * FROM ai_impact_analysis WHERE societal_group IN ('Government', 'Business') ORDER BY decision_name, societal_group
SELECT DISTINCT societal_group FROM ai_impact_analysis
SELECT * FROM societal_groups;
SELECT group_name, group_description FROM societal_groups WHERE group_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions ORDER BY decision_timestamp DESC;
SELECT decision_description FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions JOIN societal_groups ON impact_analysis_ai_decisions.societal_group_id = societal_groups.group_id;
SELECT * FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions;
SELECT decision_id, decision_description FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM societal_groups WHERE group_id BETWEEN 1 AND 5;
SELECT group_name FROM societal_groups ORDER BY group_name DESC;
SELECT MAX(decision_timestamp) AS latest_decision_timestamp FROM impact_analysis_ai_decisions;
SELECT * FROM impact_ai_decisions;
SELECT decision_name, impact_level FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group='Public';
SELECT id, decision_name, impact_level FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE id=3;
SELECT group_name, group_description FROM societal_groups ORDER BY group_name DESC;
SELECT decision_id, report_id, analysis_result FROM ethical_analysis_report WHERE group_id=1;
SELECT * FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE impact_level='High';
SELECT decision_name, ethical_analysis FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group='Government' ORDER BY decision_name DESC;
SELECT id, decision_name FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE impact_level='Low' AND societal_group='Consumer' ORDER BY id;
SELECT decision_name, impact_level, societal_group FROM impact_ai_decisions WHERE impact_level IN ('High', 'Medium') AND societal_group='Business' ORDER BY impact_level, decision_name;
SELECT * FROM ethical_analysis_report WHERE group_id=1 ORDER BY report_id DESC, decision_id ASC
SELECT * FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE decision_id = 1;
SELECT decision_description, impact FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group = 'Government';
SELECT * FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE decision_id IN (3, 5, 7);
SELECT decision_id, societal_group FROM impact_of_ai_decisions ORDER BY societal_group DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_decisions FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE impact = 'Positive';
SELECT * FROM impact_of_ai_decisions ORDER BY decision_id DESC, societal_group ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT decision_description, impact FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group = 'Minorities'
SELECT * FROM impact_of_ai_decisions WHERE societal_group IN ('Youth', 'Elderly')
SELECT decision_id, decision_description, impact FROM impact_of_ai_decisions ORDER BY decision_description ASC
SELECT decision_id, COUNT(*) AS num_decisions FROM impact_of_ai_decisions GROUP BY decision_id HAVING num_decisions > 1
SELECT * FROM impact_on_ethical_analysis;
SELECT ai_id, ai_description, ai_impact FROM ai_decisions;
SELECT group_id, group_name FROM societal_groups;
SELECT decision_description, societal_group, impact_rating FROM impact_on_ethical_analysis WHERE impact_rating > 5;
SELECT * FROM analysis_results ORDER BY group_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM analysis_results WHERE group_id = 1 ORDER BY result_id DESC;
SELECT ai_description, ai_impact FROM ai_decisions WHERE ai_impact > 50;
SELECT decision_id, decision_description, societal_group FROM impact_on_ethical_analysis WHERE impact_rating < 3 ORDER BY decision_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_feedback JOIN analysis_results ON user_feedback.result_id = analysis_results.result_id WHERE feedback_id = 1;

SELECT group_name, COUNT(*) AS number_of_decisions FROM societal_groups JOIN analysis_results ON societal_groups.group_id = analysis_results.group_id GROUP BY group_name HAVING number_of_decisions > 2;
